📘 Brand Battle — Build & Launch Plan + README

============================================================
🚀 10-Day Build & Launch Roadmap (React + Python)
============================================================

Tech Stack:
-----------
- Frontend: React.js + TailwindCSS + Zustand + React Three Fiber
- Backend: FastAPI (Python) + PostgreSQL + Redis
- AI: OpenAI / Langchain
- Deployment: Vercel (Frontend), Render or Railway (Backend)

Day-by-Day Execution Plan:
---------------------------

🗓️ Day 1: Project Setup
- Setup GitHub monorepo (frontend, backend)
- Init Vite + FastAPI project templates
- Setup CI/CD with Vercel + Railway
- Configure .env, mock data, theme setup
- Finalize folder structure

🗓️ Day 2: UI Components & Routing
- Layouts: Header, Footer, Sidebar, Theme toggle
- Pages: Home, Compare, Product, About, Login
- Setup React Router, Framer Motion, responsive layout

🗓️ Day 3: Backend API Core
- Products, Compare, Categories APIs
- User Auth (JWT)
- PostgreSQL models and schema

🗓️ Day 4: Frontend-API Integration
- Zustand for global state
- API service setup
- Product listing + search + filter

🗓️ Day 5: AI Assistant + Comparison Logic
- Integrate OpenAI or Langchain endpoint
- Comparison logic: feature-based scoring, pricing, review summary
- Set up background worker (e.g. Celery)

🗓️ Day 6: Comparison UI
- Two-column comparison card view
- Feature match score + chart
- Verdict summary + pros/cons card

🗓️ Day 7: Notifications + Wishlist
- Bookmark products
- Track price drops (mock logic or API)
- User reviews, reactions

🗓️ Day 8: Animation & Polish
- Framer Motion transitions
- Product card hover/fade-in animations
- Mobile layout fixes

🗓️ Day 9: Deployment & SEO
- Vercel + Railway deploys
- Custom domain & SSL
- Meta tags, sitemap, robots.txt
- Google Search Console setup

🗓️ Day 10: Final Testing + Launch
- End-to-end testing (Playwright/Cypress)
- Video demo + landing copy
- Launch on Reddit, Product Hunt, and index with Google


==========================================
📄 README.md (Root of GitHub Repo)
==========================================

# Brand Battle 🥊 — Product Comparison Web App

A modern AI-powered web app to help users choose the best product based on features, price, reviews, and performance.

## 🔧 Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js, TailwindCSS, Zustand, React Three Fiber
- Backend: FastAPI (Python), PostgreSQL, Redis
- AI Integration: OpenAI (Langchain), product analysis engine
- Hosting: Vercel (Frontend), Railway/Render (Backend)

## 📁 Monorepo Structure
```
root/
├── frontend/       # React app
├── backend/        # FastAPI app
├── docs/           # Diagrams, roadmap, architecture
└── README.md
```

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Frontend
```
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Backend
```
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## 🧠 Features
- Product search and filtering
- Side-by-side AI-enhanced product comparison
- Real-time verdicts and scoring system
- 3D animations and modern UI
- User wishlist + price tracking
- Light/Dark/Maroon/Teal themes

## 🛠️ Contributing
Pull requests welcome. For major changes, open an issue first.

